{"tid":1826160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又一城關閉逾兩個月重開　多個設施仍圍封須維修","createTime":"2020-01-16T01:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T06:24:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"37ccf1c70e8494e7539819c48b5067ceaa0a7e96","tid":1826160,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"九龍塘又一城去年於反修例示威期間，於11月12日遭大肆破壞後，宣布關閉逾兩個月維修，至今日（16日）早上7時終重開。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早到現場視察，約上午9時，有不少市民經連接港鐵的出口進入商場範圍，惟商場內近九成商舖仍未營業，僅銀行及超級市場開門營業。商場內多個樓層的扶手電梯以圍欄、膠布圍封，有工程人員在場維修，被破壞的玻璃圍欄則改設白色圍欄。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月12日晚上，有大批穿黑衣的示威者進入九龍塘又一城商場，破壞多個樓層的扶手電梯並擊碎玻璃圍欄、部分店舖亦遭縱火以及聖誕樹被焚燒。又一城其後宣布須進行維修而關閉，至今日7時方重開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3862199/org/7eb35ecc7f70ef59030e7da336165df2.jpg/CXYMLBRmS2qCxwepcV8USca1YEqVXGZiOLd_PDi3fzw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3862199%2Forg%2F7eb35ecc7f70ef59030e7da336165df2.jpg%2FCXYMLBRmS2qCxwepcV8USca1YEqVXGZiOLd_PDi3fzw&h=26d01db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3862200/org/5f5f6631decdee9823c9976bcd130a7a.jpg/kOj-mcMhxTihe2loaBXZzltZUIXpt7pxZPVGfGT1Rnw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3862200%2Forg%2F5f5f6631decdee9823c9976bcd130a7a.jpg%2FkOj-mcMhxTihe2loaBXZzltZUIXpt7pxZPVGfGT1Rnw&h=5a7ecf26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3862201/org/68bb3b3961a41ec2de1d945738c5d6c2.jpg/zqCw8uFufh7-W9X24RzKH64Lx5iWud4PqxplYqsaZWI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3862201%2Forg%2F68bb3b3961a41ec2de1d945738c5d6c2.jpg%2FzqCw8uFufh7-W9X24RzKH64Lx5iWud4PqxplYqsaZWI&h=a64207f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3862204/org/ca57103fb7bd9e9008714a1d832ab105.jpg/iU-h4su3mjYR2L6VKQeca3g3V0qiKEmi_w2yof8NsqE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http